ns1:ServiceCareSummaryDestination.ns1:name: Dental Emergency - Bradford, West Yorkshire (Unplanned Booking Service)
ns1:ServiceCareSummaryDestination.ns1:address: Horton Park Avenue, Bradford, West Yorkshire, BD7 3EG
ns1:ServiceCareSummaryDestination.ns1:notes:
Disposition Instructions: HOW IS A REFERRAL MADE TO THIS SERVICE? Please send an ITK message to provider at the end of the call and advise the caller that a member of staff from the booking service will contact them within 2 hours in order to arrange the next available appointment, however please note that if the caller contacts 111 between 2300-0700hrs then they will not be contacted until the service re-opens.
THIS IS A TELEPHONE BOOKING SERVICE ONLY PLEASE DO NOT DIRECT THE CALLER TO THE ADDRESS LISTED.
EXCLUSIONS: No instructions specified
INFORMATION TO GIVE TO THE CALLER: This is a booking service for unplanned dental appointments in West Yorkshire.

ns1:ServiceCareSummaryDestination.ns1:name: Community Nursing - Early Start, Leeds (Health Visitor)
ns1:ServiceCareSummaryDestination.ns1:address: Middleton Health Centre, Middleton Park Avenue, Leeds, LS10 4HT
ns1:ServiceCareSummaryDestination.ns1:notes:
Disposition Instructions: HOW IS A REFERRAL MADE TO THIS SERVICE? Give caller the telephone number and to telephone the service directly. Electronic ITK referrals are NOT currently accepted.
EXCLUSIONS: This service is only available to under 5s
INFORMATION TO GIVE TO THE CALLER: If the health visitor is out of the office, please ask the caller to leave a message on the answering machine and the Team will respond.
